showBrowserVendor.description: Define if the browser name is displayed. Default `true`

showBrowserVersion.description: Define if the browser version is displayed. Default `true`

vendor.description: Vendor of button. Default `""`, can be `firefox`, `chrome`, `iexplore`, `safari`, `opera`, `maxthon`, `flock`

imgFilter.description: The filter property defines visual effects (like blur and saturation) to an element (often ).
